reviewText: A Really good Punjabi movie. All actors in the movie were great. Diljit Dosanjh is always entertaining. That includes his acting, dancing and singing.
Cute story and love the actors. Punjabi movies are the best!!

If you need a good laugh..go for this one. Good clean fun. Even my non-Punjabi speaking daughter loved it. The songs are catchy and were downloaded to the iPods almost as soon as the movie got done.

Hope this is useful :)
